data.description: Welcome to this amazing home located in the desirable Valley Lakes community. Step inside and be greeted by the bright and inviting atmosphere of the living area. The floor plan seamlessly connects the living room, dining area, and kitchen, creating the perfect space for entertaining friends and family. The large primary bedroom is a true retreat, complete with an attached bath for added convenience and privacy. The full basement provides ample storage space and endless possibilities for additional living areas or a home gym. Plus, you'll love the convenience of having a park just a short stroll away, providing endless opportunities for outdoor recreation. For nature enthusiasts, this home is ideally located near forested areas, allowing you to explore and appreciate the natural beauty of the surrounding landscape. Whether you enjoy hiking, biking, or simply taking leisurely walks, you'll find plenty of options to connect with nature right at your doorstep. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this Valley Lakes gem your own. Schedule a showing today and experience the best of Round Lake living in this exceptional home.
